    <content>&lt;b&gt;Operations Research&lt;/b&gt; &lt;br&gt;Theorem 3 of the paper Online Allocation and Pricing: Constant Regret via Bellman Inequalities (Operations Research 69(3):821–840) states a constant regret result for a menu-pricing problem. In this erratum, the authors correct the theorem’s proof.</content>
